You are working on the PFSA public website — the public-facing site for a nonprofit.

Tech: React 19, Vite, Tailwind v4, Supabase, TypeScript, Stripe
Deploy: Vercel (dev port 3300)

Conventions:
- Folder naming: lowercase-with-dashes
- Git branch: always main
- Commits: descriptive present tense
- No TODO comments, no console.log in committed code
- TypeScript strict mode
- Production-grade code only

Design standard:
- Bold typography, distinctive colors, motion/animations
- Never generic AI aesthetics (no Inter font, no purple gradients)
- Warm, approachable nonprofit branding